The paper deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques for extracting security entities and their relationships from text, which is a common problem in the field of cyber security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also deals with cyber security concepts, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
